Dialogue: 100,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Uniform!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.57,0:00:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with this project?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:10.07,0:00:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an exposé of lust, isn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.86,0:00:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the kind of extras these are.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.11,0:00:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, she's already stripping!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.66,0:00:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.24,0:00:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a fish to water.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's get this installment started!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.58,0:00:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(30,363,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Nurse!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your shot.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your IV.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.09,0:00:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi, all of your bedpan needs!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.09,0:00:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not old enough to need that!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.14,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,Lucoa's properly dressed for once.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.05,0:00:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not too bad, I guess.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.10,0:00:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Miss Kobayashi, I asked you\Nto please stop pinching my behind!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.31,0:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's naughty!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't pinch you.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to take your temperature.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.23,0:00:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not like this—
Dialogue: 100,0:00:55.99,0:00:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! She has no pulse!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.24,0:00:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rub rub.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Beginning CPR.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait! I'm alive!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now for mouth-to-mouth.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.21,0:01:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need anymore!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.92,0:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(22,356,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon High School Girl!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late, I'm late!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.80,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wicked.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.13,0:01:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, Kanna, you're too cute. That's wicked.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.68,0:01:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, I'm, like, mega stoked.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.80,0:01:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How come?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.26,0:01:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm with Miss Kobayashi, I literally can't even.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's mad wicked.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.18,0:01:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's just too epic.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.31,0:01:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You should, like, make her your bae.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.02,0:01:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she friendzones me, I'll be highkey devastated.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.32,0:01:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If she does, we totally gotchu. We're bros.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.69,0:01:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Totes.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.57,0:01:37.36,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,You guys are my squad.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.57,0:01:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1085)}This isn't what I wanted to see.{I never asked for this much cringe.}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(28,362,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Cabin Attendant!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.33,0:01:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, please.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fasten your seatbelts.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.33,0:01:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll guide you on your\Njourney through the skies!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.12,0:01:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Lucoa?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're keeping your clothes on.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be taking off shortly.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, is there anything that we can get you?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:57.22,0:02:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ma'am! If you pinch my behind again,\Nwe'll need to escort you off of this flight!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, nobody's pinching you.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(25,359,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Police!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bike squad, move out!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.52,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, or I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohru, that's not a uniform, \Nit's a variety show costume.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi, you're under arrest!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, I'm innocent!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now to execute you.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.57,0:02:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At least hold a trial!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.66,0:02:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(25,359,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Maid!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.16,0:02:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No change here.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi, leave all the housework to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.79,0:02:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to Lady Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna, you're really not interested.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And Tohru, this is how you usually are.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess so!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.89,Default,,0,0,20,,Nothing but an apron?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.80,Default,,0,0,20,,I figured, since there were maids like this...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.68,Default,,0,0,20,,There are not!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maid, dispose of her!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Again?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the same ending as last time, isn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.40,0:02:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief, Lucoa never learns.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.06,0:02:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We should really stop inviting her for these.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Someone else is taking the next shift.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There are shifts?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.49,0:03:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, we'll see you next time,\Nfor {\i1}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Battle{\i0}.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.24,0:03:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't spoil it!
