Comment: 1,0:00:29.92,0:00:29.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnDK Nouveau Crayon\c&H363829&\1a&H1F&\blur0.75\fs80\an2\frz332.4\pos(204.069,406.287)}MEDICINE